  Locus:
    Chapter: 4
    Paragraph: 16
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: In The World Of Men
---
Confucius said, "Goodness, how could that do? You have too many
policies and plans and you haven't seen what is needed. You will
probably get off without incurring any blame, yes. But that will be as
far as it goes. How do you think you can actually convert him? You are
still making the mind  your teacher!"
